TITLE: Episode 28 - #NotMyCircus
DESCRIPTION: Maddie and Jessie touch on the inane current events that are shaping our political sphere, talk about the Deep State and their mouthpiece shill media puppets, and how whiny members of the Right and Left are really just the same.
